OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FDisabled children: Most    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fcarers not offered         
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fassessment                 
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Almost two-thirds of people who care   
OL,6, for disabled children have not been    
OL,7, offered an assessment of their needs,  
OL,8, according to a new report.             
OL,10,FGillian Baranski of Care Inspectorate  
OL,11,FWales called it unacceptable and said  
OL,12,Fshe was disappointed by the findings.  
OL,14,FThe report looks at how well local     
OL,15,Fauthorities, working with partners,    
OL,16,Fhelp disabled children.                
OL,18,FThe Welsh Local Government Association 
OL,19,Fsaid it contained positives, but also  
OL,20,F"some difficult messages".             
